track_title: Track from the ferry jetty on Kerrera

track_notes: From passenger ferry, south to NM82312803. Turn right up hill on track. Keep right of the farm through field to gateway at NM82162784. Follow track and quad route to spring NM81762804, then to col NM81612816. From here turn sharp left up a small reentrant to avoid the bog at the col. After that there are various routes, with some evidence of a quad track, to reach the summit. Fine view point.
